Package org.variantsync.diffdetective.analysis

Class CommitHistoryAnalysisTask

java.lang.Object
org.variantsync.diffdetective.analysis.CommitHistoryAnalysisTask
All Implemented Interfaces:
Callable<AnalysisResult>
Direct Known Subclasses:
EditClassValidationTask, MiningTask
public abstract class CommitHistoryAnalysisTask extends Object implements Callable<AnalysisResult>
Abstract base class for tasks to run during a HistoryAnalysis. A CommitHistoryAnalysisTasks purpose is to process a given set of commits with a specific analysis.
Author:
Paul Bittner
